---
// /about/ — Phase 5.1 (2026-05-04). Team narrative, not solo-operator.
// Endorsed Sub-Brand of Agni Consulting. Operator bench from BCG, Big Four, Series-A/B SaaS.
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About &mdash; A team of operators, by Agni Consulting | Agni AI Store"
  description="Agni AI Store is the customer-lifecycle service of Agni Consulting. A North American team of marketing-operations operators with a decade of experience inside Series-A and Series-B B2B SaaS, plus a network of consultants from BCG, McKinsey, Bain, and Big Four firms."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="ai-hero">
    <p class="ai-eyebrow">ABOUT</p>
    <h1>By operators. <br>Backed by consultants. <br>Built for service businesses.</h1>
    <p class="ai-lead">
      Agni AI Store is the customer-lifecycle service of <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> &mdash; a North American marketing-operations practice. We&rsquo;re a team of operators who&rsquo;ve shipped this stack inside venture-backed B2B SaaS, backed by a network of consultants from BCG, McKinsey, Bain, and Big Four firms. We brought it down to where it&rsquo;s genuinely needed: owner-operated service businesses across Canada and the United States.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- The team -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">The team</p>
      <h2>Operators who&rsquo;ve shipped this exact stack &mdash; at scale.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:18px;">
        Our core team is marketing-operations and demand-generation operators with a combined decade-plus of experience inside Series-A and Series-B B2B SaaS companies. We&rsquo;ve wired HubSpot, Marketo, Salesforce, Outreach, Clay, GA4, Looker, Mixpanel, and the rest of the modern revenue stack &mdash; the unsexy plumbing that decides whether a company hits its number or doesn&rsquo;t. We took that operating discipline and built it for the businesses that need it most: independent vet clinics, chiro practices, dental offices, med-spas, HVAC operators &mdash; the ones who don&rsquo;t have a CMO and don&rsquo;t want one.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        For engagements that need additional depth &mdash; pricing strategy, market sizing, regulatory navigation, change management &mdash; we tap a network of senior consultants from BCG, McKinsey, Bain, Deloitte, EY, PwC, and KPMG. Specialists, on call, drawn into engagements where the strategic question is bigger than the operational one. You don&rsquo;t pay for a 50-person agency org-chart you&rsquo;ll never use; you get the right specialist for the job.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        Every engagement is run by a senior operator who is the same person from the audit call through the monthly check-in. No SDR, no junior, no handoff to an account manager who didn&rsquo;t hear the problem.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bench at a glance -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">The bench</p>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Specialists drawn from the firms that built the modern playbook.</h2>
      <div class="ai-grid-3">
        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>Marketing operations</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);">Operators with experience inside Series-A and Series-B B2B SaaS &mdash; demand gen, RevOps, marketing-ops infrastructure, attribution, lifecycle automation. The people who&rsquo;ve actually wired HubSpot, Marketo, Salesforce, and Outreach end-to-end.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>Strategy &amp; market</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);">Senior consultants from BCG, McKinsey, and Bain available for engagements that need market sizing, pricing strategy, competitive positioning, or organizational change management beyond what an operator-led implementation requires.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>Audit, finance &amp; risk</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);">Big Four alumni (Deloitte, EY, PwC, KPMG) for engagements that touch financial reporting, audit readiness, regulated-industry compliance posture, or vendor due diligence on our infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>AI &amp; automation engineering</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);">Engineers fluent in Twilio, n8n, HighLevel, OpenAI, Anthropic, and Synthflow / Vapi / Retell. Voice-AI training, custom integrations with legacy PIMS / FSM / EMR systems, workflow orchestration that doesn&rsquo;t break when the input changes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>Industry domain</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);">For engagements in regulated verticals we tap operators who&rsquo;ve worked inside vet groups, dental DSOs, chiro / physio practice networks, HVAC consolidators, and med-spa chains &mdash; the people who know the rules, the software, and the team-shape from the inside.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-card" style="border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-soft);">
          <h3 style="color:var(--accent);">One operator runs your engagement.</h3>
          <p>The bench is in the background. Your day-to-day point of contact is a single senior operator from kickoff through cancellation &mdash; not a rotating cast of account managers. You always know who answers your email.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The relationship -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">Parent brand</p>
      <h2>How Agni AI Store relates to Agni Consulting.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:16px;">
        <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> is the parent practice. It serves B2B SaaS companies $5M&ndash;$50M ARR with on-demand marketing leadership &mdash; fractional CMO, demand-gen overhauls, marketing-ops audits, RevOps integration. Different audience, same operating standard, same bench.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        Agni AI Store is the productized service-business arm. We take the same operational backbone &mdash; lifecycle ops, automation, AI agents, integration plumbing &mdash; and apply it to vet clinics, chiropractors, dental practices, med-spas, HVAC operators, and the dozens of other owner-operated service businesses that have the same operational gaps as a Series-A SaaS company.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        Two domains, two distinct ICPs, one team, one quality bar. If you&rsquo;re looking for fractional CMO or B2B SaaS marketing-ops work, that&rsquo;s on the <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> site. If you&rsquo;re an owner-operator running a service business, you&rsquo;re in the right place here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Geography -->
  <section class="ai-section-tight">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">Where we work</p>
      <h2>North America today. Globally over time.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:16px;">
        The team is anchored in Toronto. We serve clients across Canada and the United States, with engagements in Europe by referral. We invoice in USD by default; Canadian clients can opt into CAD. Twilio numbers are local to your area code regardless of where the team sits. Data residency, HIPAA BAAs, and PIPEDA-aware practices are configured per-engagement &mdash; details on the <a href="/trust/" style="color:var(--accent);">trust page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Talk to a senior operator.</h2>
      <p class="ai-lead">No SDR. No junior. No discovery deck. The 30-minute audit is with a senior operator who could run your account if it lands.</p>
      <div class="ai-cta-row">
        <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book the audit &rarr;</a>
        <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Agni Consulting</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
